This section provides an overview of how to install GlusterFS.

*GlusterFS Installation Overview*

1.  Check the
http://www.gluster.org/community/documentation/index.php/Gluster_3.2:_Understanding_the_GlusterFS_License[GlusterFS
License].
2.  Verify that your system matches the minimum system requirements. For
more information, see
http://www.gluster.org/community/documentation/index.php/Gluster_3.2:_Checking_GlusterFS_Minimum_Requirements[Checking
Minimum Requirements].
3.  Complete the installation procedure corresponding to your
environment. Refer to
http://www.gluster.org/community/documentation/index.php/Gluster_3.2:_Installing_GlusterFS_Server[Installing
GlusterFS Server] for more information.

